<HL>
   Heilig-Meyers' June Sales Rose
</HL>
<DATE>
07/06/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C18
</SO>
<CO>
   HMY
</CO>
<LP>
   RICHMOND, Va. -- Heilig-Meyers Co., a furniture retailer,
said its June sales rose 28% to $31.4 million from $24.5
million a year earlier. Sales at stores open at least one
year increased 17%.
